<text top="2219" left="73" width="421" height="50" font="font1" id="p1_t48" reading_order_no="47" segment_no="7" tag_type="text">at  gunpoint  as  they  fled  the </text>
<text top="2263" left="71" width="424" height="50" font="font1" id="p1_t49" reading_order_no="48" segment_no="7" tag_type="text">Alliance  advance.  “A  few </text>
