<text top="2570" left="72" width="647" height="52" font="font1" id="p1_t56" reading_order_no="55" segment_no="8" tag_type="text">come  undone.  The  swiftness  of  the  re- </text>
<text top="2614" left="72" width="647" height="50" font="font1" id="p1_t57" reading_order_no="56" segment_no="8" tag_type="text">gime’s  retreat  from  the  north  led  some  al- </text>
