<text top="2531" left="771" width="649" height="46" font="font6" id="p1_t78" reading_order_no="79" segment_no="11" tag_type="text">forces  mobilized  behind  Hamid  Karzai,  a </text>
<text top="2572" left="771" width="649" height="50" font="font1" id="p1_t79" reading_order_no="80" segment_no="11" tag_type="text">commander  who  supports  the  exiled  King </text>
