<text top="291" left="1472" width="651" height="51" font="font4" id="p1_t92" reading_order_no="93" segment_no="3" tag_type="text">tions  in  the  hills  in  the  east.  A  delegation  of </text>
<text top="335" left="1471" width="649" height="51" font="font4" id="p1_t93" reading_order_no="94" segment_no="3" tag_type="text">tribal  elders  led  by  Abdul  Hagqiq,  a  former </text>
