<text top="424" left="1471" width="650" height="49" font="font2" id="p1_t95" reading_order_no="96" segment_no="3" tag_type="text">with  Taliban  representatives  negotiating </text>
<text top="467" left="1471" width="650" height="50" font="font1" id="p1_t96" reading_order_no="97" segment_no="3" tag_type="text">the  handover  of  Kandahar  and  three  other </text>
<text top="511" left="1472" width="648" height="50" font="font1" id="p1_t97" reading_order_no="98" segment_no="3" tag_type="text">southern  Afghan  provinces.  Under  the  plan, </text>
<text top="558" left="1698" width="422" height="46" font="font6" id="p1_t98" reading_order_no="99" segment_no="3" tag_type="text">Mullah  Nagqib,  an  ex-com- </text>
